    "## Fallback: heuristic judge (no LLM required)\n",
    "\n",
    "If the Databricks-hosted judge is unavailable, run this cell instead.  \n",
    "It checks for two of the most detectable failure modes without an LLM:\n",
    "- **Missing quotes** — a structural signal the output may not be grounded in the source text\n",
    "- **Evaluative language** — terms that signal the agent has stepped outside neutral analysis\n",
